  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a592eed1dd8d70541bab08fb72741cbc, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  infoTitle: Maci Salbatici
  infoText: "\u201EMaci s\u0103lbatici\u201D este o pictur\u0103 ce surprinde frumuse\u021Bea
    delicat\u0103 a naturii prin culorile vii ale florilor de mac. Tabloul eviden\u021Biaz\u0103
    atmosfera lini\u0219tit\u0103 a unui c\xE2mp plin de flori, oferind o senza\u021Bie
    de calm \u0219i libertate. Prin combina\u021Bia de culori \u0219i detaliile naturale,
    lucrarea transmite prospe\u021Bime \u0219i armonie."
